  "fun_fact": "Xylitol is the only sweetener that actively fights tooth decay! Cavity-causing bacteria can't digest it, so it starves them and prevents cavities. In Finland, kids get xylitol gum after school meals as part of a national dental health program. But keep it away from dogs - it's highly toxic to them!"
